item.description: Come join us at Harbor Park for a great night out in the field!! A lot of Nurses and good looking girls are going to be at this venue tonight which will be great for social proof. Most importantly gentlemen is that we will HAVE FUN! We can practice our game for one last summer night in the field. I want to see you all attend it's gonna be great and it's actually my favorite summer time spot. Ask anyone from this area Harbor Park on Sunday is where it's happening so let's get our game faces on and do this!
item.how_to_find_us: I will be the tall guy with Red Hair.
item.name: Harbor Park In Middletown!
